WEBVTT

00:01:28.517 --> 00:01:30.826
Guess what? No one knows.

00:01:32.167 --> 00:01:35.760
Most of those questions
puzzle me more now than ever.

00:01:35.784 --> 00:01:38.287
But diving into them is exciting

00:01:38.311 --> 00:01:40.594
because it takes you
to the edge of knowledge,

00:01:40.618 --> 00:01:42.618
and you never know what you'll find there.

00:01:43.921 --> 00:01:49.497
So, two questions that no one
on Earth knows the answer to.

00:01:50.704 --> 00:01:52.389
(Music)

00:01:52.413 --> 00:01:56.112
[How many universes are there?]

00:01:57.812 --> 00:01:59.976
Sometimes when I'm on a long plane flight,

00:02:00.000 --> 00:02:02.868
I gaze out at all those
mountains and deserts